      <description sparkle:format="plain-text"><![CDATA[- Fixed a Sparkle relaunch regression where `Install and Relaunch` could fail to reopen the app if a Finder-style relaunch (`-psn_`) was incorrectly treated as a settings-handoff launch.
- Restricted running-instance settings handoff to explicit `--settings` launches only, while preserving "click app icon to open Settings" behavior for normal Finder/Dock launches.]]></description>
